#29104
{BO,BL}Entrance To Themiscyra{bo,bl}~
{BO,BL}
   Two age-darkened wooden gates bar entrance into the city of
   Themiscrya. Sharp metal spikes protrude from the sturdy
   wood, darkened further by trails of dried blood. The tips of
   numerous arrows poke through crescent-shaped holes in the
   stone blocks forming the city's walls. A look to the top of
   the gates shows a stone battlement, also lined by archers.
{bo,bl}
