#29105
{BO,BL}The Battlement{bo,bl}~
{BO,BL}
   The battlement is usually lined with archers. They serve not
   only as defenders of the city but also as scouts, for from
   this vantage point they can easily see ships sailing in from
   the Black Sea to the north. The pulley to open the gates
   below is also located here.
{bo,bl}
