#29106
{W}Otrera Road{w}~
{W}
   The street, named after the Queen's mother, is broad but
   unpaved. Trees grow haphazardly all around the road, and
   give one the sense of being in a forest. Few people are
   on the streets. Too few, for a city of this size. Amazons
   do not like being confined within walls, apparently.
{w}
