{W}Otrera Road{w}~
{W}
   This part of Themiscrya is more densely populated than the
   parts to the west. Wooden houses appear regularly, but each
   is well-landscaped and positioned to provide the best vista
   possible. The residents seem well-armed: besides some women
   in long robes, every other woman on the street is carrying
   either a spear or a bow.
