#29113
{BO,BLU}Open Air Markets{bo,blu}~
{BO,BLU}
   From merchants hawking their wares to Amazons bargaining for
   a better price, the noise in this market is deafening. Some
   merchants wait on their customers in large, semi-permanent
   stalls while others make their deals over little more than a
   blanket on the ground. This is the only place in the city
   where men are regularly seen.
{bo,blu}
