#29120
{BO,BL}A Wooden House{bo,bl}~
{BO,BL}
   This wooden house is sparsely furnished with well-crafted
   items. In the far corner, rich fur pelts line a heavy oak
   bed. An black iron cooking pot hangs in the now-cold hearth.
   The table next to the hearth holds gold plates and goblets,
   no doubt plundered from an Amazon foe. Windows in every wall
   are an attempt to make the inhabitant feel a part of the
   great outdoors.
{bo,bl}
