#29126
{BLU}The Horse Trader{b}~
{BLU}
   The horse trader is the most welcome merchant in the market,
   since Amazons are highly skilled riders who see horses as an
   inseparable part of their lives. Today, he is showing five
   horses, which are tied to stakes around his tent. They are
   all excellent animals, as Amazons would accept nothing less
   than the best.
{blu}
