{BLU}A Market Stall{blu}~
{BLU}
   This uncovered stall sells only weapons used by Amazons. Two
   women stand by the spears, hefting each in turn. Some others
   are testing the fine bows crafted by the weaponsmith. Yet
   another is talking to the weaponsmith, an unstrung bow in
   hand, no doubt discussing the cost of fixing her weapon.
{blu}
