{G}An Overgrown Forest{g}~
{GR}
   This is an old-growth forest, with trees rising so high it
   is impossible to see the treetops. There are no discernible
   paths through the forest. Even worse, the canopy blocks out
   the sunlight and any view of landmarks. The trunks of these
   trees are often so thick that they block progress in certain
   directions.
