{BO,W}The Temple of Artemis{bo,w}~
{BO,W}
   Wide, gradual steps lead up to the Temple of Artemis. The
   crescent-shaped building is a white so pure that it gleams,
   as befits the virgin goddess. Ionic columns define the edge
